videos.description: Eric Paschall powers his way through three defenders on his way to the lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Paschall powers through the lane for the layup) 2019// ESHEET

videos.headline: Paschall powers through the lane for the layup

videos.description: Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree gets the rebound and tips the ball in with the clock expiring sending Villanova into halftime with a 28-26 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nova ends the half on a last-second, tip-in shot to take the lead) 2019// ESHEET

videos.headline: Nova ends the half on a last-second, tip-in shot to take the lead

videos.description: Saddiq Bey makes a great defensive play with the block, then finds an open Jermaine Samuels in the corner for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bey’s block leads to Samuels 3) 2019/03/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bey's block leads to Samuels 3

videos.description: Seton Hall misses the 3-pointer to win and the tip-in shot to tie as Villanova holds on to win the Big East Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Seton Hall gets 2 chances but can’t hit a shot to win) 2019/03/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Seton Hall gets 2 chances but can't hit a shot to win
